{"word":"H7290 - רָדַם - râdam - raw-dam' - Sleep","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָדַם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>râdam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>raw-dam'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Sleep"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆயாசமாய்த் தூங்கு. அயர்ந்த நித்திரைபண்ணு, உறங்கு, தூங்கு, அயர்ந்த நித்திரைகொள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(Niphal) to be asleep, to be unconscious, to be in heavy sleep, to fall into heavy sleep, to be fast asleep"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>stun</i>, that is, <i>stupefy</i> (with sleep or death): - (be fast a-, be in a deep, cast into a dead, that) sleep (-er, -eth)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1719 - דְּדָן - Dᵉdân - ded-awn'/1719\">H1719</a>, <a href=\"#/H1721 - דֹּדָנִים - Dôdânîym - do-daw-neem'/1721\">H1721</a>, <a href=\"#/H7290 - רָדַם - râdam - raw-dam'/7290\">H7290</a>, <a href=\"#/H8639 - תַּרְדֵּמָה - tardêmâh - tar-day-maw'/8639\">H8639</a>"}]}